Ogg-LibOgg version 0.02
=======================

Perl Module to give access to libogg functions.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires NO other modules but DEPENDS on libogg library.

You will have to install libogg and libogg-devel in Linux and only 
libogg in Mac to make this module work (please use your discretion). 

Mac OS:
sudo port install libogg

Linux:
sudo yum install libogg
sudo yum install libogg-devel

Windows:
Not Sure, never tested or tried :-)

